@node Main "Abstracon - Documentation"

                          'Abstracon' 1.0

                        by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Abstracon' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} where you have to place various
tiles that have 'abstract' or random patterns in each of the game
boards. The idea is that the tiles must make a path from the entry,
located at the top of a game board, to the exit, which is located
at the bottom... Also, you have to place tiles on all spaces of a
game board.

  Complete each game board in the least amount of moves.

  Have fun!

